### 景德镇旅游智能推荐系统 API 测试

### 1. 获取所有景点
GET http://localhost:8889/api/scenic

### 2. 获取景点详情
GET http://localhost:8889/api/scenic/1

### 3. 获取推荐景点
GET http://localhost:8889/api/scenic/recommend

### 4. 根据分类获取景点
GET http://localhost:8889/api/scenic/category/博物馆

### 5. 根据标签搜索景点
GET http://localhost:8889/api/scenic/search/tag?tag=陶瓷

### 6. 根据名称搜索景点
GET http://localhost:8889/api/scenic/search/name?name=古窑

### 7. 根据价格范围搜索景点
GET http://localhost:8889/api/scenic/search/price?minPrice=0&maxPrice=50

### 8. 用户注册
POST http://localhost:8889/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "tourist",
  "phone": "13800138888"
}

### 9. 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8889/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "tourist1",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 10. 获取所有用户
GET http://localhost:8889/api/user

### 11. 创建评论
POST http://localhost:8889/api/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "scenicSpotId": 1,
  "content": "这是一个测试评论",
  "rating": 5
}

### 12. 获取景点评论
GET http://localhost:8889/api/review/scenic/1

### 13. 创建订单
POST http://localhost:8889/api/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "merchantId": 1,
  "scenicSpotId": 1
}

### 14. 获取用户订单
GET http://localhost:8889/api/order/user/2

### 15. 创建商家
POST http://localhost:8889/api/merchant
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "shopName": "测试店铺",
  "description": "这是一个测试店铺"
}

### 16. 获取所有商家
GET http://localhost:8889/api/merchant